{"tid":525891,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我想知仲有幾多舊香港人係度","createTime":"2018-01-11T06:45:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-13T03:46:04.000Z","uid":92230,"like":18,"dislike":39,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"66fd25a9686ff8881f04de5cdbc48e30d6b71234","tid":525891,"uid":92230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T06:45:56.000Z","msg":"留言講下大家中幾多樣<br />\n<br />\n1. 唔用支那詞，唔寫殘體字 (<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/520160/\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/520160/</a>)<br />\n2. 唔用淘寶 (<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/466892/\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/466892/</a>)<br />\n3. 唔上大陸玩 (指周邊地區，諸如西藏，上海等除外) (<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/521615/\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/521615/</a>)<br />\n4. 覺得自己係香港人，大於，覺得自己係中國人<br />\n5. 聽到內地人用普通話交談覺得唔舒服<br />\n6. 知道商家或餐廳係中資或者源自內地會有負面印象甚至罷買罷食<br />\n7. 新認識一個內地人，既定第一印象係負面<br />\n8. 聽到負面新聞 (例如工廠爆炸，黑心工場，見死不救)，第一反應覺得係關中國事<br />\n9. 有意識分清楚媒體是否親中，會強烈懷疑親中媒體既內容，例如香港01，巴士的報，TVB<br />\n10. 認同喺香港應該香港人優先 (例如買樓，學位等)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我估計平均應該中7樣<br />\n利伸，中9樣，唔中第3樣，因為條女想去無計"},{"pid":"8ee5b1ba1330c0ef681423ea89806a4bfcd01140","tid":525891,"uid":92230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T06:49:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5ba5a57c546200ca2edbdcb224b88964b15f547","tid":525891,"uid":41116,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T06:51:22.000Z","msg":"你條戇鳩<br />\n內地人唔係支那詞？<br />\n不嬲叫大陸人，近幾年叫支那人"},{"pid":"117359f125752c34dcad6c2f56a6c770195a6576","tid":525891,"uid":10637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T06:52:21.000Z","msg":"我中10樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21cac8e4df6ecb2aad7eaad5f272cce6311e41b3","tid":525891,"uid":65530,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T06:52:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2